features: 【A4 Hardcover Spiral Journal Notebook】 Large a4 size 8.5"x11" notebook, standard 7mm space classic college ruled journals. The professional durable water-resistant plastic hard cover will protect your notebooks to last for years, which has oil-resistant and anti-bending properties, effectively protecting the internal paper of the journal and provides a comfortable writing surface.

【100 GSM Ink-friendly Paper】 Our blue spiral notebook pages are very thick, which avoids ink bleeding through and ghosting. Suitable for most pen types, such as ballpoint pens, fountain pens. Each lined journal 55 sheets/110 pages, offering enough space to write in. Allowing you to write on both sides of every page to maximize your usable space. light ivory paper is not dazzling, let you have a comfortable writing experience.

【Upgrade Lined Journal Notebook 】Come with an elastic closure band, works as bookmarks. Equipped with a removable ruler and personal information page, makes it easy to keep track of queries. The back cover includes an expandable pocket for cards and note-taking notes. Tabbed sticky notes and a handy pen loop holder are included. “Memo No” and “Date” are at the top of each page for classification and reference.

【Strong Spiral Metal Twin-Wire】 Our spiral journal notebook has a sturdy gold-color double wire spiral with easy-to-turn pages and keeps pages attached reliably, while still staying flat when opened, which reading more convenient and taking notes more efficient. Spiral bound journal easy to tear-off and fold over, as well as flip the cover back, giving you a better writing experience. Golden spiral bound adds aesthetic matching, it’s the perfect big notebook for journaling, and planning.

【Multiple Usage & After Sale】 Blue spiral journal perfect for school, office, home, work organization, college, students, adults, travelers, business executives, scientists, and people in many other fields. Suitable for writing journals, study, diary journals, drawing, sketching, travel journals, work notebooks or for taking notes in college classes or meetings. If you encounter quality problems, please contact us, we will give you a full refund or replacement!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Quality and pleasure to use
reviews.reviewText: Wish I had one of these in every size and design pattern for different kinds of work and note taking/drawing. Paper is nice quality and the large size and spiral at the top makes it great for left handlers.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice notebook - cover is not opaque
reviews.reviewText: The product arrived quickly. The pages feel nice and the additional features like the elastic band and pocket are a bonus. I specifically bought this notebook as it was advertised as “hard cover.” The cover is a somewhat see-through plastic that is fairly flexible. I believe it will still hold up well, but you can see anything written on the first page through the cover. I downgraded to 4 stars for this reason, as there was no indication in any description or picture that the cover would not be opaque. In the picture you can see that writing on the first page shows clearly through the cover.

reviews.reviewTitle: Not even close to description and not worth the price
reviews.reviewText: Bought this because it was listed and described as a hardcover notebook. It's not. Not even close. It's bumpy thin flexible plastic that I have no doubt will crack. It's a cheaper version of the Hilroy notebooks for 3x the price. I have had sturdier notebooks from a dollar store. Don't bother. It's not even worth the 6.50 import fee.
